01:01:05.000 --> 01:01:18.000
The observers are used to track the organization of the focus group, how the moderator behaves, how deep the essence of the respondents is revealed, and so on

01:01:18.000 --> 01:01:31.000
In the room where the focus group is held, there is usually a round or oval table to create a warm atmosphere, even a home environment

01:01:31.000 --> 01:01:47.000
Respondents are offered cooling drinks, sometimes coffee and tea, sometimes even a small snack, because the focus group is held in the evening, after work

01:01:47.000 --> 01:02:07.000
The respondents are motivated to come to the company's office after work or to the office where the focus group is rented, and spend 1.5-2 hours, sometimes more, discussing and talking about, for example, washing powder

