01:03:17.000 --> 01:03:23.000
How many groups should be held for a specific research project?

01:03:23.000 --> 01:03:30.000
It all depends on the problem and the range of problems that are solved with the focus group

01:03:30.000 --> 01:03:38.000
But most often, one problem, one research question is solved by 4-6 focus groups

01:03:38.000 --> 01:03:47.000
The focus groups stop their work when new high-quality information ceases to be received

01:03:47.000 --> 01:04:00.000
