01:07:35.000 --> 01:07:53.000
The sphere of application of design methods is the testing of naming, especially interesting names and company names, design, ideas, and concepts, assessment of positioning of the company's products, for example, the composition of the perception map

01:07:53.000 --> 01:08:12.000
When the consumer is offered to draw and place in different cells that reflect the range of the consumer's attitude to a new product, a new brand, to draw coordinate axes in the cells and place competing brands and products on them

