01:10:42.000 --> 01:11:05.000
First, a moderator must address participants during the discussion, because participants can demonstrate different types of behavior, some will be silent, some active, those who are more active do not always make constructive suggestions, and a silent participant, on the contrary, may hide some constructive thoughts that may be interesting for the purpose of the research

01:11:05.000 --> 01:11:26.000
