01:11:48.000 --> 01:12:10.000
That is why a moderator must be persistent and able to interrupt such an active participant. There are many different psychological methods of interruption, it can be simply to switch the gaze from one to another, you can ask to insert, to highlight a moment during the speech of this silent expert

01:12:10.000 --> 01:12:33.000
And ask other members of the focus group to join in the discussion, or to object, to try to interrupt this conversation, or you can take extreme measures, and if you see that you cannot manage the discussion because of this participant, you can invite him out of the room, but not just like that

