01:22:57.920 --> 01:23:16.920
I must say that very often respondents try to answer such questions, because they take no more than a few seconds. If such a phone survey takes more than 50-15 minutes, then respondents need to be motivated additionally

01:23:16.920 --> 01:23:30.920
