01:24:35.920 --> 01:24:59.920
What is good about such surveys, which are called CATI, Computer Assisted Telephone Interview, is that immediately, every minute after the start of the survey, you can see the cumulative result of the information collection

01:24:59.920 --> 01:25:27.920
At the same time, there are restrictions on the use of such surveys, because a large number of respondents refuse to participate, and secondly, there cannot be a large number of questions in such a survey, because the time for conducting a phone interview is always limited not by its cost, but by the fact that respondents get tired of answering such questions

01:25:27.920 --> 01:25:52.920
In addition, the questions that are intended for a phone interview in the survey should be extremely simple, extremely understandable, and should contain a small number of answers, most often, these are only closed questions with answers, and the answers are always very simple, very easy to read or heard

01:25:52.920 --> 01:26:09.920
